Currently the following is outputted:

{noformat}
2007-05-15 20:09:32,115 WARN [resin-tcp-connection-0.0.0.0:28801-17] [opensymphony.xwork.util.OgnlValueStack] findValue Caught an exception while evaluating expression 'xHtmlComments' against value stack
 -- url: /pages/diffpagesbyversion.action | userName: anonymous | action: diffpagesbyversion | page: 9206
java.lang.RuntimeException: Caught an Ognl exception while getting property xHtmlComments
        at com.opensymphony.xwork.util.CompoundRootAccessor.getProperty(CompoundRootAccessor.java:112)
{noformat}

What I dont have is enough information to reconstruct the request -- the query string is missing, so I don't know which versions they were diffing. When I plod through myself, it all looks fine. Having a link that needed less construction (even if it's relative - i.e. missing the protocol, domain and servlet context) would really help.

The viewuser.vm file should have the following:
{noformat}
<a href="mailto:$!user.email">$!user.email</a>
{noformat}
not:
{noformat}
<a href="mailto:$$!user.email">$!user.email</a>
{noformat}

Cheers,
Justin

