I often find myself needing to link to a user, but not knowing what Confluence user id they chose. I'd really like to be have an 'Insert User" button like the "Insert Image" and "Insert Link" buttons. Another option would be to have a "Users" tab on the "Insert Link" dialog. Either way, the UI would let you search by name for the user you wanted, and then click on their name to add the link.

